<Desc><entry>A structured education programme for people with Type 2 diabetes.  Offers information and education in a group setting to enable people to understand their condition and thus manage it.  Offers the programme to all patients with Type 2 diabetes and also runs courses for South Asian (Urdu/Punjabi speaking) people with interpreters.  Courses are free.  Referral is by practice nurse/GP.</entry>
